OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FOrder to stop border checks
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fbased on 'sound legal      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fadvice' - Poots            
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Edwin Poots has said his order to stop 
OL,6, Irish Sea border checks was based on   
OL,7, "sound legal advice", which he said    
OL,8, would now "be tested" in court.        
OL,10,FSpeaking in the assembly, the DUP      
OL,11,Fagriculture minister also defended his 
OL,12,Fdecision to seek independent advice    
OL,13,Ffrom a constitutional lawyer, paid for 
OL,14,Fby his department.                     
OL,16,FHe said he was satisfied the advice    
OL,17,Fprovided the basis for his instruction.
OL,19,FDespite the order, checks have         
OL,20,Fcontinued at Belfast and Larne ports.  
